column14: Cells were seeded in full media; the following day media was changed to either estrogen depleted media (for DMSO and E2 groups) or same DMEM/F12 50/50 full media (for FM); cells were incubated for 72h; the day of cell harvesting media was refreshed
column16: Cells were crosslinked in adherent conditions, crosslinked cells were lysed to obtain nuclear extracts, lysates were clarified from sonicated nuclei and protein-DNA complexes were isolated with antibody.
column17: ChIP-seq reads were filtered for quality and 3' trimmed for adapter sequences using trimgalore, Reads were aligned to mouse assembly hg38 using bowtie2 (v2.2.2) with default parameters., Read count tables were created using featureCounts v1.6.0., To create density files, the signal was normalised using the scalefactors from DESeq2 converted to BigWig using BEDTools.
